                        <div class="card-header">
                            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                                <div class="col-md-8">
                                    <div class="header-text">
                                        <h2 class="card-title">2mergency 앱을 방문하신것을 환영합니다</h2>
                                        <h4 class="card-subtitle">건강한 라이프를 꿈꾸는 분들과 함께합니다</h4>
                                        <hr />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-5 ml-auto">
                                    <div class="media">
                                        <div class="media-left">
                                            <div class="icon">
                                                <i class="nc-icon nc-circle-09"></i>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="media-body">
                                            <h4>자유로운 가입</h4>
                                            <p>2mergency 앱과 함께 다양한 기능을 무료로 활용하실수있습니다</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="media">
                                        <div class="media-left">
                                            <div class="icon">
                                                <i class="nc-icon nc-preferences-circle-rotate"></i>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="media-body">
                                            <h4>등산, 산책, 운동 메이트</h4>
                                            <p>혼자 힐링하면서 또는 그룹과 어울려 운동메이트와 함께하세요</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="media">
                                        <div class="media-left">
                                            <div class="icon">
                                                <i class="nc-icon nc-planet"></i>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="media-body">
                                            <h4>랜덤한 산책안내</h4>
                                            <p>원하시는 만큼 반경에서 자유롭게 산책길을 추천합니다</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4 mr-auto">      
                                    <form action="/auth/register" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                                        <div class="card card-plain">
                                            <div class="content">
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <label class="__2m__form-label">닉네임</label>
                                                    <input
                                                    type="text"
                                                    name="nickname"
                                                    placeholder="닉네임"
                                                    class="form-control"/>
                                                </div>
                                                <label class="__2m__form-label">이메일</label>
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <input
                                                    type="email"
                                                    name="email"
                                                    placeholder="이메일"
                                                    class="form-control"/>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <label class="__2m__form-label">패스워드</label>
                                                    <input
                                                    type="password"
                                                    name="password"
                                                    placeholder="패스워드"
                                                    class="form-control"/>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <label class="__2m__form-label">패스워드확인</label>
                                                    <input
                                                    type="password"
                                                    name="passwordConfirm"
                                                    placeholder="패스워드확인"
                                                    class="form-control"
                                                    />
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <label class="__2m__form-label">주소</label>
                                                    <input
                                                    type="text"
                                                    name="address"
                                                    placeholder="주소"
                                                    class="form-control"
                                                    />
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <label class="__2m__form-label">프로필이미지</label>
                                                    <input class="form-control"  accept="image/*" name="profileImage" type="file" id="formFile" placeholder="프로필이미지">                             
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                                                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="isOpen" id="isOpen" value="true">
                                                <label class="__2m__form-label"  for="inlineRadio1">공개활동</label>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                                                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="isOpen" id="isOpen" value="false">
                                                <label class="__2m__form-label" >비공개활동</label>
                                                </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="footer text-center">
                                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-fill btn-neutral btn-wd">가입하기</button>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </form>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
